Package: dictare
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libportaudio2, portaudio19-dev
Recommends: ydotool
Maintainer: dragfly <dragfly@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Voice-first control for AI coding agents
 dictare captures audio from your microphone, transcribes it using
 Whisper, and controls AI coding agents (Claude Code, Cursor, Aider)
 via the OpenVIP protocol.
